episodes.title: Leader of cult-like group linked to multiple killings arrested in Maryland
episodes.description:
The leader of the so-called "Zizians" - a cultlike group which is connected to a series of violent incidents across the country - has been arrested in Allegany County, Maryland.

READ MORE: https://foxbaltimore.com/news/city-in-crisis/cult-like-group-linked-to-multiple-killings-and-recent-arrest-in-maryland#
